WEBVTT

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.268
saya berteriak,

00:10:30.292 --> 00:10:32.559
"Semuanya tutup mulut
dan turuti perintahku!

00:10:32.583 --> 00:10:34.143
Kalian semua parah!

00:10:34.167 --> 00:10:36.393
Aku akan mengambil ponsel
dan camilan kalian

00:10:36.417 --> 00:10:39.601
dan segala hal yang kalian nikmati
di dalam hidup!"

00:10:39.625 --> 00:10:41.101
(Tertawa)

00:10:41.125 --> 00:10:42.434
Anda pernah mengalaminya?

00:10:42.458 --> 00:10:45.851
(Tepuk tangan)

00:10:45.875 --> 00:10:48.500
Volatilitas, meremehkan.

00:10:49.417 --> 00:10:52.351
Si sulung berbalik dan menatap,
saya lalu berkata,

00:10:52.375 --> 00:10:53.976
"Bu, itu namanya bukan cinta."

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:57.351
(Tertawa)

00:10:57.375 --> 00:11:00.268
Saya sempat sangat marah
karena kritikannya itu.